      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014not a scratch in sight and that 'new car' smell is still going strong. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it because I truly love cars, and I know you will too. It\u2019s smooth, shiny, and ready for a new home. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
