    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2017 Ford Focus RS, finished in Nitrous Blue. This specimen features the 2.3L EcoBoost inline-four, utilizing a low-inertia twin-scroll turbocharger and a high-flow cylinder head to produce a linear power band. The Ford Performance AWD system is the centerpiece, equipped with a GKN-sourced Rear Drive Unit that employs twin electronically controlled clutch packs for dynamic torque vectoring. The chassis is completely factory-spec, retaining the dual-mode adjustable dampers and Brembo four-piston monoblock front calipers for optimal thermal management during spirited driving. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service dossier, the critical cylinder head gasket recall was performed by master technicians using the revised components. The vehicle remains in stock configuration, riding on original forged alloy wheels. The interior is immaculate, featuring Recaro shell seats with pristine bolsters and no signs of UV degradation on the dash or trim.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
